events.name: 華麗なるギャンブラー1-7

parameters: Bouncer at the gambling den: 'Miss, who referred you?'

Bouncer at the gambling den: 'We don't allow walk-ins. Since
you already know about this place--'

Priestess Sophia: I wonder if it's okay to say your name,
that playful person... hehe, a noble...
Gambling den bouncer: Could it be...?

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, let's refrain from mentioning each
other's names, shall we?

Priestess Sophia (I don't know if such a person exists,
though)
Skilled gambler: Miss, that place is a special gambling den.

Skilled gambler: Do you have the qualifications for that...?
How about we have a match here first?
Priestess Sophia: Understood, I'll handle it gently.

Skilled gambler: Shall we play a simple game? How about a
game of High and Low?

Skilled gambler: Games like this really test a person's
luck, you know.

Priestess Sophia: It doesn't matter what we wager. By the
way, what would you like to bet?

Skilled gambler: Here, the minimum is 50,000G. You didn't
come empty-handed, right?

Priestess Sophia: I don't have any money, but if you have
something worth more than 50,000G, I have that.

Skilled gambler: Please spare me the trouble of exchanging
it for cash.

Priestess Sophia: If there is anything you desire, feel free
to do as you please with my body if I were to lose.

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, it seems your eyes have changed. I
will show you my victory against all three of you here.
後ACT：ミニゲーム「ハイアンドロー」

Priestess Sophia: Oh my, is this what the gambling hall here
is like?

Priestess Sophia: If there are no gamblers better than them,
then it's about time...
Hey, miss, want to play over here?
House Manager Lance: I'm the one in charge here, I'm Lance.

Bodyguard: There are rumors that the hawk-eyed ones are
sniffing around! We don't have the luxury to engage in
gambling right now!

House Manager Lance: Life is a gamble... Can those who run
away after witnessing such intense matches call themselves
gamblers?

Priestess Sophia: I was just bored. Will you please ignite
my soul?

House Manager Lance: I'm fired up... Let's settle this one-
on-one.

This has turned into an incredible match with a skilled
gambler...

Bodyguard: It's not often that you get to witness such a
high-stakes match!

Behold, the skilled gambler...! Depending on the community
cards and my hand...

House Manager Lance: The fifth card has been revealed, what
will you do?
Priestess Sophia: Hehe, I dislike crude questions.

House Manager Lance: Let's go until the showdown, shall we?
Let's show each other our hands!
House Manager Lance: Sorry, it's a spade straight flush.

Priestess Sophia: I have a bad habit of peeking at each card
one by one, so please let me flip them over.

House Manager Lance: In order for you to beat me, you'll
need the Ace of Spades.
House Manager Lance: Now, show me your hand.
Priestess Sophia: As for the second card...
Priestess Sophia: It's the Ace of Spades!

Fuego, the Hawk's Eye: Our organization has taken control of
Malaco Village. Shall I have you come?

House Manager Lance: I don't mind being killed by you guys,
but I just want to know the final outcome as a gambler.
House Manager Lance: Miss, may I have you flip the cards?

House Manager Lance: Hahaha! It was a fun gamble befitting
the end of my life.

House Manager Lance: I'm glad that you're my final
opponent... Can I ask for your name?
Priestess Sophia: My name is Sophia.

House Manager Lance: I'll go play poker with those demons
first. Someday, let's play poker again and make our hearts
race.

House Manager Lance: May the blessings of the goddess of
victory, Actina, be upon us!
